reviewText: He certainly was king of the cowboys. I saw him in a Gene Autry film where he was featured singing in the group,the Sons of the Pioneers. Soon after that,he became a star in his own movies along with Dale Evans. It was a different time in movie history,but no one can ever replace him.
i gave this to my mother as a gift and she hasn't stoped talking about how nice the picture looks or how great it is to see roy looks. so i give this colliction 4 stars
